#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:377
msgid "Inventory"
msgstr "在庫"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/products.rst:379
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Inventory Defaults` sub-section, fill in those fields:"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`在庫デフォルト` サブセクションで、これらのフィールドに入力します。"

